      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Sales Pipeline Management Without Leaving Gmail",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is Streak's bread and butter, and it's where the tool genuinely shines.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Picture this: a prospect emails you asking about pricing. In a traditional CRM workflow, you'd copy their name, switch to your CRM tab, create a new deal, add notes, set a follow-up reminder, and then go back to Gmail to reply.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "With Streak, you do all of that ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "in the same window",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every email thread gets a box inside a customizable pipeline. You drag it from \"Lead\" to \"Qualified\" to \"Proposal Sent\" to \"Closed Won\" — just like Trello cards, but for sales. Each box stores contact details, notes, tasks, and even call logs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what makes it powerful in practice:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Color-coded stages",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " give you instant visual clarity on your entire pipeline.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
