        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've seen teams of 3 and teams of 300 use Streak pipelines daily. The magic is the same: zero friction between reading an email and updating your CRM.",
