    "image_prompt": "Editorial tech thumbnail, 16:9. Incorporate the brand logo fetched from https://logo.clearbit.com/streak.com as the clean focal element over a soft amber-to-cream gradient (Notion + Apple aesthetic). A person sitting at a laptop with Gmail open, colorful kanban pipeline columns visible on screen, coffee cup beside the keyboard, natural office lighting. Glassmorphism cards, soft volumetric light, generous negative space for a title, no embedded text, no watermark. --ar 16:9 --style raw",
    "faq_items": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Streak CRM really free?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Streak offers a free plan that includes one pipeline with up to 500 contacts, mail merge with up to 50 emails per day, and basic email tracking. It's enough to test the tool thoroughly before upgrading to Pro ($49/user/month) or Pro+ ($69/user/month) for advanced features.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Does Streak work with Google Workspace or only personal Gmail?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak works with both personal Gmail accounts and Google Workspace (business Gmail). In fact, Google Workspace users get additional benefits like shared pipelines across team members and admin-level controls for managing access and data.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can Streak replace a full CRM like HubSpot or Salesforce?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For many small to mid-sized teams, absolutely. Streak covers sales pipelines, mail merge, follow-up automation, reporting, and integrations — all inside Gmail. Teams that need deeply complex workflows with hundreds of custom objects might still prefer enterprise CRMs, but for most email-driven businesses, Streak delivers everything you need without the overhead.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
